                        <li>reduced anxiety</li>
                        <li>clearer thinking</li>
                        <li>deeper relationships</li>
                        <li>improved self-esteem and confidence</li>
                        <li>Nurturing your mental health can also help you manage health conditions that are worsened by stress, like heart disease, says Seponara.</li>
                    </ol>
